      "invocation": "/data-guardian",
      "trust_tier": "gate-keeper",
      "description": "Data privacy enforcer. Detects PII and medical data, classifies data sensitivity, blocks transmission of SENSITIVE data. Has blocking authority \u2014 SENSITIVE data blocks are never overridden.",
